Description.value:
This integration flow creates a calculated New Business quotation for auto insurance in SAP Quotation and Underwriting in Insurance. 
It also creates or updates all required objects as the business partners in the role of policy holder, premium payer and named drivers in Business Partner in SAP S/4HANA, the vehicle to be insured, and the New Business application in SAP Policy Management in SAP S/4HANA. 
Information, such as premium before and after tax, policy number, submission number, and quotation number, is returned.
